Class QuizAttemptController

java.lang.Object
com.github.ilim.backend.controller.QuizAttemptController
@RestController public class QuizAttemptController extends Object
REST controller responsible for managing quiz attempts.

Provides endpoints for students to submit quiz attempts, retrieve their attempts, and allows instructors and admins to view all quiz attempts for a specific quiz.

    • submitQuizAttempt

      @PostMapping("/student/attempt-quiz") @PreAuthorize("hasAnyRole('STUDENT', 'INSTRUCTOR')") public ApiRes<Res<QuizAttemptResultDto>> submitQuizAttempt(@AuthenticationPrincipal org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt jwt, @Valid @RequestBody @Valid QuizAttemptDto dto)
      Submits a quiz attempt by a student.

      Accepts a QuizAttemptDto containing the student's answers and quiz details, processes the attempt, and returns the result.

      Parameters:
      jwt - the JWT token representing the authenticated user
      dto - the quiz attempt data transfer object containing quiz details and answers
      Returns:
      an ApiRes containing the QuizAttemptResultDto with the results of the attempt

    • getAllQuizAttempts

      @GetMapping("/student/quiz-attempt/{quizId}") @PreAuthorize("hasAnyRole('STUDENT','INSTRUCTOR')") public ApiRes<Res<List<QuizAttemptResultDto>>> getAllQuizAttempts(@AuthenticationPrincipal org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt jwt, @PathVariable UUID quizId)
      Retrieves all quiz attempts for a specific quiz by a student.

      Fetches all attempts made by the authenticated student for the given quiz ID.

      Parameters:
      jwt - the JWT token representing the authenticated user
      quizId - the unique identifier of the quiz
      Returns:
      an ApiRes containing a list of QuizAttemptResultDto representing all attempts

    • getAllQuizAttemptsForQuiz

      @GetMapping("/instructor/quiz-attempt/{quizId}") @PreAuthorize("hasAnyRole('INSTRUCTOR', 'ADMIN')") public ApiRes<Res<List<QuizAttempt>>> getAllQuizAttemptsForQuiz(@AuthenticationPrincipal org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt jwt, @PathVariable UUID quizId)
      Retrieves all quiz attempts for a specific quiz by all students.

      Allows instructors and admins to view all quiz attempts made by students for the given quiz ID.

      Parameters:
      jwt - the JWT token representing the authenticated user (instructor or admin)
      quizId - the unique identifier of the quiz
      Returns:
      an ApiRes containing a list of QuizAttempt representing all student attempts
